    </li>
  </modExtensions>
</GeneDef>
<GeneDef>
  <defName>WestTek_Gene_AgainstTheDark</defName>
  <label>against the dark</label>
  <description>The pawn's memory is compressed into protected synthetic storage. Learning remains possible, but old data is aggressively indexed and pruned.</description>
